    "ConclusionIn conclusion, generative AI has the potential to transform orthopedic education by providing innovative tools and methodologies for enhancing learning, teaching and practical application.",
    "Using AI-driven simulations, personalized learning experiences, and advanced data analytics, educators can significantly improve the efficiency and effectiveness of orthopedic training.",
    "The integration of these technologies has the potential to address not only present educational challenges, but also provide a foundation for continuous improvement and adaptation in the rapidly evolving field of orthopedics.",
    "However, the integration of generative AI in orthopedic training is not without challenges.",
    "Issues related to bias, accuracy, and the need for substantial human oversight remain major hurdles."
